2.Get the gateway address : //run netstat -nr ![](data:image/*;base64,)
3. We now need to plug this information into the Pi&#39;s  **DHCP**  configuration file using a text editor.     //run sudo nano /etc/dhcpcd.conf
4. On the very top of the file type in the following lines:

interface eth0
static ip\_address=10.0.0.XX/24
static routers=10.0.0.1
static domain\_name\_servers=10.0.0.1

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)
